ine\nemissions, to constrain the ionisation of H, He, N and O and the flux of Lyman\ncontinuum photons from O stars in the ICM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Feb 1997 15:02:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-30"}
